3. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper briefly mentions the security of blockchain technology and its associated cryptocurrencies. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses the use of persistent homology techniques for predicting Bitcoin price dynamics, which falls under the scope of systems and control. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper discusses the use of graph features and persistent homology techniques for analyzing blockchain graphs, which falls under the scope of data structures and algorithms.
